Paper: hep-th/0004041

Date: 2000-04-06

Title: Comment on Casimir energy for spherical boundaries

Authors: I. Brevik, B. Jensen, and K. A. Milton

Comments: 5 pages, REVTeX. Typographical error corrected, acknowledgements

addedJournal-ref: Phys.Rev. D64 (2001) 088701

It is shown that recent criticism by C. R. Hagen (hep-th/9902057) questioningthe validity of stress tensor treatments of the Casimir energy for spacedivided into two parts by a spherical boundary is without foundation.